<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <h1>MetroMath</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

<div id="part-1">
  <div class="row" id="container">
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <p>Let's calculate whether you should buy an unlimited MetroCard or a regular paid card.</p>
      <p>Click start to begin.</p>
      <button id="start">Start</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="part-2">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <p>On average, how many times a day do you take the subway during the week?</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <select id="weekday">
        <option value="0">Not at all</option>
        <option value="1">Once a day</option>
        <option value="2">Twice a day</option>
        <option value="3">Three or more times a day</option>
      </select>
      <br><br>
      <button id="weekday-submit">Submit</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="part-3">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <p>On average, how many times a day do you take the subway on weekends and holidays?</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-4">
      <select id="weekend">
        <option value="0">Not at all</option>
        <option value="1">Once a day</option>
        <option value="2">Twice a day</option>
        <option value="3">Three or more times a day</option>
      </select>
      <br><br>
      <button id="weekend-submit">Calculate</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-4 answer">

  </div>
</div>

</div>
